00:00:32.299 --> 00:00:35.719
For most of them, it's the
only probability and statistics

00:00:35.719 --> 00:00:36.510
class they'll take.

00:00:36.510 --> 00:00:39.500
A lot of them will
go on to be doctors

00:00:39.500 --> 00:00:43.700
and so our goal is to have
at least statistically

00:00:43.700 --> 00:00:47.590
literate doctors out there.

00:00:47.590 --> 00:00:50.110
That's important.

00:00:50.110 --> 00:00:53.780
